                <h1>Can You Wallpaper Plaster Walls? Here's What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>Yes, you can wallpaper plaster walls, but proper preparation is key for a successful application. Ensure the walls are clean, dry, and smooth. Repair any imperfections and consider applying a primer designed for plaster to improve adhesion. Use high-quality wallpaper paste for the best results and to prevent peeling.</p>
